Memory consumption increased significantly in Prisma 7 in comparison to Prisma 6

### Bug description

We observe significant memory consumption increase after migration from Prisma 6 to Prisma 7 for Postgres.

### Severity

🚨 Critical: Data loss, app crash, security issue

### Reproduction

Following example can be considered:

```schema.prisma
generator client {
  provider = "prisma-client"
  output   = "../src/generated/prisma"
}

datasource db {
  provider = "postgresql"
  url      = env("PRISMA_TEST_POSTGRES_URL")
}

model Sample {
  time     DateTime
  sensorId String

  pressure    Float
  temperature Float

  @@unique([time, sensorId])
  @@index([time])
}

```

The test script performing following steps:
1. generate batch of data
2. insert batch into database (Postgres)
3. log memory usage
